03:54.593 --> 03:56.361
but all kinds of stuff happened.

03:56.395 --> 03:58.196
I mean, we had to play a job

03:58.229 --> 04:00.532
with Steve Mackay on drums.

04:00.565 --> 04:02.867
Which is really wild because, you know

04:02.901 --> 04:05.236
