11:08.860 --> 11:11.029
but what they finally did do

11:11.062 --> 11:13.698
was after about a year of that

11:13.732 --> 11:16.167
they just gave me the master bedroom.

11:18.202 --> 11:20.138
At the time I thought,
"Wow, this is great!"

11:20.171 --> 11:22.841
but now I realize,
also it was probably a..

11:22.874 --> 11:26.711
Probably a comparable lesser
of two tortures.

11:26.745 --> 11:28.747
And they moved a..

11:28.780 --> 11:31.349
They-they moved
a standard sized bed

11:31.382 --> 11:33.017
into the small room.

11:33.051 --> 11:35.019
No desk,
just-just enough so they could

11:35.053 --> 11:36.855
get in and out of bed.

11:36.888 --> 11:39.690
And I had a...

11:39.724 --> 11:41.325
...single bed and my drum set

11:41.359 --> 11:44.095
set up all the time
in the master bedroom.

11:44.128 --> 11:45.930
I was so lucky...

11:47.198 --> 11:50.101
...to live at close quarters

11:50.134 --> 11:53.604
in a simple environment with my parents.

11:53.637 --> 11:55.840
I got to know my parents.

11:55.874 --> 11:57.408
Uh, that's a..

11:57.441 --> 11:58.943
That's a real treasure.

