12:55.599 --> 12:58.269
I had a high school band, "The Iguanas."

12:58.302 --> 13:02.740
We got a job playin' full-time
at a teen club.

13:02.773 --> 13:05.243
A place called The Ponytail.

13:05.276 --> 13:07.946
I kept scheming, thinking of things

13:07.979 --> 13:11.916
to get more attention and,
uh, so I thought

13:11.950 --> 13:15.086
"What if I played
on the biggest drum riser

13:15.119 --> 13:17.221
that anybody has ever had?"

13:18.890 --> 13:20.624
I was about 16 feet up.

13:20.658 --> 13:23.461
All by myself, you know

13:23.494 --> 13:26.764
and the, and the band
is down there grumbling.

13:26.797 --> 13:29.600
A loser in the biz named Chuck

13:29.633 --> 13:30.768
