13:34.372 --> 13:36.474
and I'll help you
promote your own gigs."

13:36.507 --> 13:38.943
So we rented a pier for one night

13:38.977 --> 13:41.012
to throw our own concert.

13:41.045 --> 13:45.483
And we had a huge turnout,
a huge success.

13:49.053 --> 13:53.357
Until half-way through
the floor started to give.

13:55.159 --> 13:59.130
Nobody got hurt but basically,
we, we broke the pier.

14:00.498 --> 14:04.068
